Recap

• Agentless Polling: Achieves seamless, lightweight monitoring with minimal resource impact, offloading intensive tasks to monitoring servers.

• Dynamic Dashboards: Delivers actionable insights through customizable, real-time visualizations.

• Advanced Alerting & Automation Frameworks: Implements intelligent, automated responses to streamline operations and reduce manual interventions.

• Targeted Alerts: Minimizes alert fatigue by ensuring precision and relevance in notifications.

• Predictive Analytics: Leverages AI-driven analysis to proactively identify threshold breaches and prevent disruptions.

• Capacity Planning: Provides accurate forecasts for critical resources, including memory, CPU, and storage, enabling data-driven decision-making.
